title: Wolverine - Origins (001 - 050 + Annual) (2006 - 2010) (digital)
description:
Wolverine - Origins (001 - 050 + Annual) (2006 - 2010) (digital) (Minutemen-PhD)


For years Wolverine did not have access to his past memories due to brainwashing and memory implants. Now that he has regained those memories, he is attempting to sort them out. Faced with past deeds he was forced to complete, Wolverine is trying to right those wrongs and to seek out those responsible
